Note:
Runa Standard Library: HTTP Protocol Handling

Provides comprehensive HTTP protocol handling including request/response management, middleware support, routing, authentication, and advanced HTTP features.

Idiomatic Runa code uses natural language operators:
  Let request be create http request with method as "GET" and url as "http://example.com"
  Let response be send request to server
  Let middleware be add middleware to server with handler as "auth_middleware"
  Let route be add route to server with path as "/api/users"

For advanced/AI-generated code, use helpers:
  Let result be create with method as http_method and url as request_url
  Let result be add with server as http_server and middleware as handler
:End Note

